Checking
All American National checking accounts can be opened with $100 and include these benefits at no charge:
 

Online Banking � bank when and where you want!
Bill Pay � the ultimate in convenience! Plus, you save time and money.
eStatements � your statement is available for viewing sooner, you are better protected from identity theft, and you are making an environment-friendly choice. 
Unlimited American National ATM Usage � your money, when you want it!
Visa® Check Card � making purchases is easier and safer than when you carry cash. Learn about our Instant Issue Debit Cards.
Telephone Banking � get information about your accounts 24/7.

Enjoy these benefits . . . and the checking account that best meets your needs. Select from:
Premier Checking
The name says it all. This account combines all of the services you need with the extras you want:

Tiered interest rates�the higher your balance, the higher your interest rate
Preferred interest rates on CDs
First box of checks at no charge
Once per year, $10 discount on check order
Your choice of paper statements at no charge, or E-Statements
$20 annual discount on safe deposit box
Cashier�s checks at no charge
Unlimited use of non-American National ATMs at no charge (other institutions� fees may apply)
Unlimited check writing
No monthly fee for daily account balances over $5,000, or if you have a combined balance of $50,000 or more in any combination of up to five accounts with American National (including checking, savings, money market, CD, IRA accounts or a loan). ($20 monthly fee if balance falls below minimum)

Interest Checking � Apply Online Today!
Your checking account is the workhorse of your financial services . . . reward it with interest. Account includes:

Competitive interest rates
Unlimited check writing
eStatement at no cost; paper statement with check images for $3.00 per statement cycle ($2.00 with no check images)
No monthly fee for daily account balances of $1,000 or more($12 monthly fee if balance falls below minimum)

Key Checking
Enjoy all the essential checking services and a low balance requirement. Account includes:

Unlimited check writing
eStatement at no cost; paper statement with check images for $3.00 per statement cycle ($2.00 with no check images)
No minimum balance fee for daily account balances of $200 or more ($6 monthly fee if balance falls below minimum)

eChecking � Apply Online Today!
Say goodbye to regular monthly service charges and hello to your favorite electronic services. Account includes:

Eight paper checks processed per statement cycle at no charge; $0.50 charge per paper check over the limit of eight during the statement cycle
Two transactions at non-American National ATMs per month at no charge
Your choice of paper statements (with no check images) or eStatements










