051401027 Routing Number



051401027 Routing Number (American National Bank & Trust Co)
051401027 is assigned to AMERICAN NATIONAL BANK & TRUST CO, DANVILLE, Main Office by American Bankers Association (ABA). AMERICAN NATIONAL BANK & TRUST CO Main Office is located at 103 TOWER DRIVE, DANVILLE, VA. In case of any confusion regarding the routing number, one call the bank directly at (434) 792-5111.
