Company Overview of American National Bank and Trust Company



Snapshot People




Company Overview
American National Bank and Trust Company, a chartered bank, provides personal and business banking products and services in Virginia. Its personal banking products and services include checking accounts; savings accounts, including Easy Save, Christmas Easy Save, money market, premium money market, health savings, certificates of deposit, and individual retirement accounts; loans, such as home equity lines of credit, mortgages, and personal loans; credit cards; and various other services, including online services, mobile banking and mobile deposit, Apple Pay, rapid deposit, telephone banking, eStatements, check and ATM cards, and instant issue debit cards. The company’s business banking pro...
American National Bank and Trust Company, a chartered bank, provides personal and business banking products and services in Virginia. Its personal banking products and services include checking accounts; savings accounts, including Easy Save, Christmas Easy Save, money market, premium money market, health savings, certificates of deposit, and individual retirement accounts; loans, such as home equity lines of credit, mortgages, and personal loans; credit cards; and various other services, including online services, mobile banking and mobile deposit, Apple Pay, rapid deposit, telephone banking, eStatements, check and ATM cards, and instant issue debit cards. The company’s business banking products and services comprise business checking and savings accounts; credit cards; loans, including commercial loans for airplanes, agriculture, churches, construction, equipment purchases, medical practices, municipalities, owner- and non-owner occupied real estate, receivables and inventories, and commercial trucks; and business lines of credit; and treasury management and other business services. It also provides investment management, trust and estate management, financial planning, and retirement plan services; and personal and business insurance services. American National Bank and Trust Company was formerly known as American National Bank & Trust Company of Danville and changed its name in September 1984. The company was founded in 1909 and is based in Danville, Virginia. It has branch locations in Bedford, Burlington, Chatham, Collinsville, Danville, Graham, Greensboro, Gretna, Hardy, Lovingston, Lynchburg, Martinsville, Mebane, Ridgeway/220 South, Rocky Mount, South Boston, Union Hall, and Yanceyville. American National Bank and Trust Company operates as a subsidiary of American National Bankshares Inc.
Detailed Description


